The PetConnectX is a comprehensive platform designed to assist pet owners and animal rescuers by providing real-time access to
nearby veterinary clinics and animal welfare organizations. The platform enables users to report missing pets through
image-based postings and facilitates engagement through community-driven comments. Additionally, it supports emergency medical
assistance by listing nearby veterinarians and organizations that help injured or sick animals. By integrating location-based
services, interactive pet recovery features, and a collaborative support system, The PetConnectX ensures faster response times 
for lost pets and animals in need of medical attention.
